### API Test Requests / Тестові запити API
### Save as test.http and use in VS Code REST Client extension

### ============================================
### HOTELS / ГОТЕЛІ
### ============================================

### Create Hotel / Створити готель
POST http://localhost:8080/hotels
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Test Hotel 1",
  "city": "Kyiv",
  "address": "123 Test Street, Kyiv",
  "rating": 5
}

### Get All Hotels / Отримати всі готелі
GET http://localhost:8080/hotels

### Get Hotel by ID / Отримати готель за ID
GET http://localhost:8080/hotels/1

### Update Hotel / Оновити готель
PUT http://localhost:8080/hotels/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Updated Test Hotel",
  "city": "Kyiv",
  "address": "456 New Street, Kyiv",
  "rating": 4
}

### Delete Hotel / Видалити готель
DELETE http://localhost:8080/hotels/1

### ============================================
### ROOMS / НОМЕРИ
### ============================================

### Create Room / Створити номер
POST http://localhost:8080/rooms
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "number": "101",
  "type": "Deluxe",
  "pricePerNight": 150.0,
  "capacity": 2,
  "hotelId": 1
}

### Get All Rooms / Отримати всі номери
GET http://localhost:8080/rooms

### Get Room by ID / Отримати номер за ID
GET http://localhost:8080/rooms/1

### Get Rooms by Hotel / Отримати номери готелю
GET http://localhost:8080/rooms/hotel/1

### Update Room / Оновити номер
PUT http://localhost:8080/rooms/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "number": "101",
  "type": "Deluxe Suite",
  "pricePerNight": 200.0,
  "capacity": 4,
  "hotelId": 1
}

### Delete Room / Видалити номер
DELETE http://localhost:8080/rooms/1

### ============================================
### GUESTS / ГОСТІ
### ============================================

### Register Guest / Зареєструвати гостя
POST http://localhost:8080/guests
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Ivan",
  "lastName": "Ivanov",
  "email": "ivan@example.com",
  "phone": "+380501234567"
}

### Get All Guests / Отримати всіх гостей
GET http://localhost:8080/guests

### Get Guest by ID / Отримати гостя за ID
GET http://localhost:8080/guests/1

### Get Guest Bookings / Отримати бронювання гостя
GET http://localhost:8080/guests/1/bookings

### Update Guest / Оновити гостя
PUT http://localhost:8080/guests/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Ivan",
  "lastName": "Ivanov",
  "email": "ivan.new@example.com",
  "phone": "+380501234568"
}

### Delete Guest / Видалити гостя
DELETE http://localhost:8080/guests/1

### ============================================
### BOOKINGS / БРОНЮВАННЯ
### ============================================

### Create Booking / Створити бронювання
POST http://localhost:8080/bookings
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "checkInDate": "2024-05-01",
  "checkOutDate": "2024-05-05",
  "status": "ACTIVE",
  "roomId": 1,
  "guestId": 1
}

### Get All Bookings / Отримати всі бронювання
GET http://localhost:8080/bookings

### Get Booking by ID / Отримати бронювання за ID
GET http://localhost:8080/bookings/1

### Get Active Bookings / Отримати активні бронювання
GET http://localhost:8080/bookings/active

### Update Booking / Оновити бронювання
PUT http://localhost:8080/bookings/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "checkInDate": "2024-05-01",
  "checkOutDate": "2024-05-07",
  "status": "ACTIVE",
  "roomId": 1,
  "guestId": 1
}

### Cancel Booking / Скасувати бронювання
DELETE http://localhost:8080/bookings/1

### ============================================
### AMENITIES / ЗРУЧНОСТІ
### ============================================

### Create Amenity / Створити зручність
POST http://localhost:8080/amenities
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "WiFi",
  "description": "High-speed wireless internet connection",
  "hotelId": 1
}

### Get All Amenities / Отримати всі зручності
GET http://localhost:8080/amenities

### Get Amenity by ID / Отримати зручність за ID
GET http://localhost:8080/amenities/1

### Add Amenity to Room / Додати зручність до номера
POST http://localhost:8080/amenities/rooms/1/amenities/1

### Remove Amenity from Room / Видалити зручність з номера
DELETE http://localhost:8080/amenities/rooms/1/amenities/1

### Delete Amenity / Видалити зручність
DELETE http://localhost:8080/amenities/1

### ============================================
### SEARCH / ПОШУК
### ============================================

### Search Hotels / Пошук готелів
GET http://localhost:8080/search/hotels?query=kyiv

### Search Rooms / Пошук номерів
GET http://localhost:8080/search/rooms?query=deluxe

### Search Guests / Пошук гостей
GET http://localhost:8080/search/guests?query=ivan

### ============================================
### ANALYTICS / АНАЛІТИКА
### ============================================

### Get Hotels Count / Отримати кількість готелів
GET http://localhost:8080/analytics/hotels/count

### Get Rooms Count / Отримати кількість номерів
GET http://localhost:8080/analytics/rooms/count

### Get Active Bookings / Отримати активні бронювання
GET http://localhost:8080/analytics/bookings/active

### Get Completed Bookings / Отримати завершені бронювання
GET http://localhost:8080/analytics/bookings/completed

### Get Rooms by Type / Отримати номери за типом
GET http://localhost:8080/analytics/rooms/by-type

### Get All Analytics / Отримати всю аналітику
GET http://localhost:8080/analytics/all

### ============================================
### HEALTH & METRICS / ЗДОРОВ'Я ТА МЕТРИКИ
### ============================================

### Check Service Health / Перевірити стан сервісу
GET http://localhost:8080/actuator/health

### Get Metrics / Отримати метрики
GET http://localhost:8080/actuator/metrics

### Get Prometheus Metrics / Отримати Prometheus метрики
GET http://localhost:8080/actuator/prometheus

